changes i made to the kernel
1.edit the syscall_64.tbl file
	arch/x86/entry/syscalls/syscall_64.tbl
add a new line for your system call
	454	common	spar10pidances		sys_spar10pidances

2.add system call prototype to header file
	include/linux/syscalls.h
add a new line before the last #endif in the file
	asmlinkage long sys_spar10pidances(pid_t pid)

3.write your actual code in
	kernel/spar10pidances.c

4.add entry in the kernel Makefile
	kernel/Makefile
the entry should be added to the obj-y  
	obj-y += spar10pidances.o

5.make again
